Japanese chef scoops top award in London
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
LONDON, Nov 15, 2009 (AFP)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tomoyuki Abe of Japanese restaurant chain Sushizen was named best chef at a
