The Eat-Japan Sushi Awards 2009 featured seven of the world's best sushi chefs
preparing their favourite dishes. Invited guests then tasted the foods before
picking the winner through a ballot.
</P>
<P>
The event, described by organisers as "the Oscars of the sushi world", was won
last year by Mitsunori Kusakabe of the Sushi Ran restaurant in California,
United States.
</P>
