Ok heres one. DD168 Maddox. Served with the USN until 1941. Then transfered to the Royal Navy as HMS Georgetown under the lend/lease plan and then a further transfer to the Russian Navy as Doblistni and then returned to the Royal Navy again in 1952. Hows that for a go around? <img src="http://www.worldaffairsboard.com/images/smilies/smiles.gif"/>
