Elvis had 149 songs on the Billboard Hot 100 Pop Chart. Of these, 114 were in the Top 40; 40 were in the Top 10; and 18 went to Number 1.
With those 114 Top 40 hits, Elvis had two times as many hits as any other artist in the rock era.

